OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering partner
OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FA jury has found a Whitehaven man
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering his partner in a
OL,8,F'distressing' attack.
OL,10,FPaul Irwin, 50, of George Street,
OL,11,FWhitehaven, has been convicted of
OL,12,Fmurdering Tiffany Render, 34, after
OL,13,Fcausing her to collapse from a
OL,14,Fhaemorrhage at his flat on 22 March
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FCarlisle Crown Court heard how Miss
OL,18,FRender, described as a vulnerable
OL,19,Fwoman, was "trapped inside an
OL,20,Faggressive violent and controlling
OL,21,Frelationship".
