OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering partner
OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FProsecutor Iain Simkin KC said:
OL,7,F"Tiffany Render had become conditioned
OL,8,Fto obedience, was in thrall to the
OL,9,Fdefendant and, irrespective of the
OL,10,Frisks to her own wellbeing,
OL,11,Fnevertheless visited him on 22 March."
OL,13,FThe jury found Irwin guilty after
OL,14,Fnearly four hours of deliberations on
OL,15,F22 November 2024.
