OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering partner
OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FA pathologist detailed how Miss
OL,7,FRender, who was 5ft 1in and weighed
OL,8,Fless than nine stone, suffered
OL,9,Frepeated blunt force trauma "again and
OL,10,Fagain" - it is expected Miss Render
OL,11,Fdied within an hour of the attack.
OL,13,FIrwin, who's 5ft 10in and weighs 17
OL,14,Fstone, was described as "off his head"
OL,15,Fwith drink and cocaine during the
OL,16,Fincident.
