OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering partner
OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FThe jurors heard how Irwin was handed
OL,7,Fa suspended prison sentence for
OL,8,Frepeatedly hitting Miss Render with a
OL,9,Fwooden rolling pin, as well as
OL,10,Fslapping and strangling her.
OL,12,FIn the weeks before her murder, Irwin
OL,13,Fhad been arrested twice and bailed on
OL,14,Fthe condition not to contact Miss
OL,15,FRender.
OL,17,FJudge Mrs Justice Foster discharged
OL,18,Fthe jury from crown court for life
OL,19,Fafter acknowledging the "distressing"
OL,20,Fdetail of the trial.
