OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering partner
OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FDuring evidence, Irwin said that he
OL,7,Fsuffered from schizophrenia, insisting
OL,8,Fhis condition was medicated and under
OL,9,Fcontrol in March.
OL,11,FThe 50-year-old claimed Miss Render's
OL,12,Fdeath was accidental. He pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to manslaughter and sexual
OL,14,Fassault during evidence. He will be
OL,15,Fsentenced next month.
