OL,4,Cin 'horrific' attack
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Matt Scott,
OL,7,FSenior Investigating Officer of the
OL,8,Fcase, said: "This was a horrific crime
OL,9,Fand Irwin subjected Tiffany Render to
OL,10,Fan aggressive, violent, and
OL,11,Fcontrolling relationship.
OL,13,F"After hearing all the evidence
OL,14,Fgathered against Irwin by officers, a
OL,15,Fjury found him responsible for
OL,16,FTiffany's death.
