OL,6,F"I would like to thank the members of
OL,7,Fthe jury ` ordinary members of the
OL,8,Fpublic- who have sat and listened
OL,9,Fcarefully to some shocking evidence in
OL,10,Fthis case and returned a guilty
OL,11,Fverdict.
OL,13,F"I would also like to thank our
OL,14,Fcolleagues within the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service and prosecuting
OL,16,Fcouncil Iain Simkin KC for the manner
OL,17,Fin which the case has been prepared
OL,18,Fand delivered at trial.
