OL,6,F"Finally, I must thank the dedicated
OL,7,Fteam of police officers and staff who
OL,8,Fhave worked tirelessly on this
OL,9,Finvestigation. They have shown great
OL,10,Fprofessionalism throughout."
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Scott says
OL,13,Fhis thoughts are with Tiffany's family
OL,14,Fand friends "at this incredibly
OL,15,Fdifficult time."
OL,17,FHe said: "I would finally like to
OL,18,Fthank and pay tribute to Tiffany's
OL,19,Ffamily. They have been dignified
OL,20,Fthroughout the course of the
OL,21,Finvestigation.
